亚胡与特朗普通话 讨论重启对伊战事可能性。⑥阿联酋巴拉卡核电站外围一处发电机遭无人机袭击起火。⑦美媒：伊朗计划收取霍尔木兹海峡海底光缆通行费。</span>","source_link":""},"important":1,"tags":[],"channel":[1,3],"remark":[{"id":98434303,"url":"https://miniprogram.jin10.com?path=/pages/redirect/redirect&data=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&id=57909&type=8","icon":"","type":"miniProgram","thumb":"https://img.jin10.com/mp/26/05/ekxB0_F1sWyYIkHnRHWN2.jpg","title":"金十数据整理：昨日今晨重要新闻汇总（2026-05-18）","secType":8,"objectID":57909}],"extras":{"ad":false}},{"id":"20260518062128858800","time":"2026-05-18 06:21:28","type":0,"data":{"pic":"","title":"","source":"新华社","content":"【美国得州首府发生多起随机枪击事件致4人受伤】金十数据5月18日讯，美国得克萨斯州首府奥斯汀市周末发生至少10起随机枪击事件，案发地点包括消防站等地，造成4人受伤。据美媒17日报道，当地警方官员称，枪击案发生于周六夜间至周日清晨，嫌疑人在逃窜途中疑似多次盗取车辆。","vip_level":0,"source_link":"https://h.xinhuaxmt.com/vh512/share/13106110?docid=13106110&newstype=1001&d=13526a6"},"important":0,"tags":[],"channel":[1,3],"remark":[],"extras":{"ad":false}},{"id":"20260518060522768800","time":"2026-05-18 06:05:22","type":0,"data":{"pic":"","title":"","source":"","content":"现货黄金站上4550美元/盎司，日内涨0.26%。","source_link":""},"important":0,"tags":[],"channel":[1,2],"remark":[{"id":32459558,"type":"quotes","title":"现货黄金","symbol":"XAUUSD.GOODS","content":"请升级APP后查看"}],"extras":{"ad":false}},{"id":"20260518060446302800","time":"2026-05-18 06:04:46","type":0,"data":{"pic":"https://flash-scdn.jin10.com/flash_dli/jin_fanti/img/878fc396-4878-8b74-f8fa-1779055207438.jpg","title":"","source":"","content":"【美联储6月维持利率不变的概率为99.2%】金十数据5月18日讯，据CME“美联储观察”：美联储到6月维持利率不变的概率为99.2%，累计降息25个基点的概率为0.8%。美联储到7月维持利率不变的概率为95.0%，累计降息25个基点的概率0.7%，累计加息25个基点的概率为4.2%。","source_link":""},"important":0,"tags":[],"channel":[1,2,3],"remark":[{"id":80778119,"pic":"https://flash-scdn.jin10.com/flash_dli/jin_fanti/img/878fc396-4878-8b74-f8fa-1779055207438.jpg","url":"https://miniprogram.jin10.com?path=/pages/redirect/redirect&attr_id=0&category=interestRateForecast&data=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&id=59091&type=1","icon":"https://cdn.jin10.com/assets/minipro/icons/longPic.png",